 school that doubts his encounters with the evil Lord Voldemort are legitimate. The seventh and final book in the series, "Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows," is still scheduled for release July 21. Send feedback about IndyStar.com Use of this site signifies your agreement to the Privacy Policy/Your California Privacy Rights , updated August, 2006. Copyright 2007 IndyStar.com. All rights reserved .Build 0: 16 ms (Misc) .Build 9: 15 ms (Content)
